GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 19th January, 2011
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 19th January,
2011:
(i)
The Prime Minister relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Culture;
(ii)
Shri Sharad Pawar relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Consumer Affairs, Food and Public Distribution and
assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Food Processing
Industries. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the
Minister of Agriculture;
Shri Virbhadra Singh relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Steel and assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of Micro, Small and Medium Enterprises;
(ii)
Shri Vilasrao Deshmukh relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Heavy Industries and Public Enterprises and assumed
the charge of the office of the Minister of Rural Development and
the additional charge of the office of the Minister of Panchayati Raj;
(iv)
Shri S. Jaipal Reddy relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Urban Development and assumed the charge of the
office of the Minister of Pe
